# Track the source lib manifest. The generic `lib/` rule above is meant for
# setuptools build dirs; ucc-gen emits vendored libraries into output/ (ignored),
# so the requirements manifest under package/lib/ must stay version-controlled.
!package/lib/
!package/lib/requirements.txt

# Local Splunk test files
local/
*.log
